//### ============================================
//### LLM 모델 관리
//### ============================================

### 현재 LLM 모델 상태 조회
GET {{host}}/api/settings/model
Accept: application/json

### 사용 가능한 Provider 목록
GET {{host}}/api/settings/model/providers
Accept: application/json

//### ============================================
//### LLM Provider 변경
//### ============================================

### Anthropic Claude로 변경
POST {{host}}/api/settings/model
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "anthropic"
}

### OpenAI GPT로 변경
POST {{host}}/api/settings/model
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai"
}

